<plot>This short in Universal's "Sing and Be Happy" series (production number 1382) stars Joey Faye and singer Suzanne Tafel. She phones Faye's radio shop to have him repair her radio. Fayes shows up, some slight comdey ensues, he fixes the radio and the songs begin. Songs, with the radio-supplied music, include "My Blue Heaven" and Suzanne and a chorus doing "Whispering" and "Oh, Johnny."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?366554</url></doc>
